$timescale 1ns $end
$comment
  JTAG Pro decoder error-detection fixture.
  Six scan groups:
    1. IDCODE scan                  (clean)
    2. IDCODE DR scan + TRST abort  (RED — Scan aborted by TRST)
    3. BYPASS scan                  (clean)
    4. DR scan with X on TDI        (RED — X/Z value on TDI)
    5. SAMPLE/PRELOAD IR scan       (clean)
    6. IR scan glitched by X on TMS (RED — indeterminate TAP)
  Each red transaction is bracketed by a green control scan
  so the comparison is obvious in the transaction table.
  Regenerate via: dart run tool/generate_jtag_error_fixture.dart
$end
$scope module tb $end
$var wire 1 ! TCK $end
$var wire 1 @ TMS $end
$var wire 1 ^ TDI $end
$var wire 1 & TDO $end
$var wire 1 % TRST $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
$dumpvars
0!
0@
0^
0&
1%
$end
